NG0549:452: bzhes shig bzhengs shig chos kyi dbyings las bzhengs //
NG0549:454: snyan gsan rang 'od dal du bzhengs //
NG0549:455: 'og min lhun grub pho brang nas //
NG0549:456: dus gsum bde gshegs 'jam dpal bzhi bcu gnyis //
NG0549:457: longs sku mtshan dang dpe byang rdzogs pa'i sku //
NG0549:458: dus gsum bde gshegs spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NG0549:459: thugs rje lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing *//
NG0549:460: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan 'dren na //
NG0549:461: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nyas gnas bskyod la //
NG0549:462: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rtogs bral dges pa bskyed //
NG0549:463: e h+ye hi b+ha ga ban ma ha ka ru ni ka kri sha ho /
NG0549:465: phyag rgya bzhi yi 'od zer las //
NG0549:466: bar snang mkha' la sprin phung bzhin //
NG0549:468: gnyis med bstim zhing gzhugs su gsol //
NG0549:469: lha dang gnyis su bdag med la //
NG0549:470: rtog pa'i lus kyis phyag kyang btsal //
NG0549:471: bde gshegs 'od zer lus rtog bcom //
NG0549:472: rnam bzhi don ldan phyag rgyas mchod //
NG0549:473: kun bzang dbyings nas mchod pa sprul //
NG0549:474: che ba'i yon tan bdud rtsis mchod //
NG0549:475: rang las 'od bsdus dngos grub blang *//
NG0549:477: ye shes chos nyid gang zhing rgyas //
NG0549:478: 'do yon drug gis bsam pa gang *//
NG0549:480: ba lim gtor ma'i mchod pa 'bul //
NG0549:481: ma ha ba ling ta pu dza ho /
NG0549:482: bdag dbang rdo rje brtan pa'i sku //
NG0549:483: lnga rdzogs bde ba gcig tu 'khyil //
NG0549:484: rang 'byung lnga dang mdzes pa'i ro //
NG0549:486: pany+tsa a mri ta pu dza ho /
NG0549:487: chos nyid bde bas mdzes gang la //
NG0549:488: khams gsum bsgral ba'i rag ta la //
NG0549:489: dngos med ye shes mchod par sbyar //
NG0549:490: rag ta chags pa'i mchod par 'bul //
NG0549:491: ma ha rag+ta pu dza ho /
NG0549:493: khams gsum yongs su bsgral nas kyang *//
NG0549:494: log rtog chos nyid dbyings su rol //
NG0549:495: khams gsum yongs sgrol mchod par 'bul //
NG0549:496: sarba ta tha ga ta dz+nya a be ram ram a yam spa ra na phat /
NG0549:498: thabs dang shes rab ro mnyam gcig / kun tu bzang mo yum gyi mkha' //
NG0549:499: ye shes thig le gcig tu 'khril //
NG0549:500: ma chags pad+ma sbyor ba'i mchod par 'bul //
NG0549:504: thabs dang shes rab chos dbyings las //
NG0549:505: las chen sbyor ba'i yul dbang bsgrol //
NG0549:506: ting 'dzin shugs mchod chu rgyun bsgyur //
NG0549:507: byin rlabs shugs ldan mchod pas mchod //
NG0549:508: phyogs bcu ma lus bde gshegs zhing *//
NG0549:509: sna tshogs rin chen mdzes pa'i 'od //
NG0549:510: mnyen 'jam reg bya bde ba'i mchog / lha mo bsam yas bro gar glu //
NG0549:511: dbyibs legs mdog sdug sgra dbyangs ldan //
NG0549:512: rol mo sil snyan 'phan gdugs dang *//
NG0549:513: bla re rgyal mtshan lhab lhub dang *//
NG0549:514: rin chen 'dod yon sna tshogs bsnams //
NG0549:515: sems las dbang bsgyur thabs lam pas //
NG0549:516: chos kyi dbyings nas rang sprul nas //
NG0549:517: rig pa'i rang dbang rgyun mi 'chad //
NG0549:518: tshangs pa'i gnas su mchod rgyun khyil //
NG0549:519: bdag nyid bdag la rol zhing mchod //
NG0549:520: skye ba med pa'i dbyings su thim //
NG0549:521: ye shes glu dang rol mos mchod //
NG0549:522: lha dang bdag nyid rdzas rnams dang *//
NG0549:523: kun kyang byang chub sems nyid yin //
NG0549:524: smon lam ye shes rgya mtshor brlab //
NG0549:525: gnyis med bsgrubs la 'gro don bshad //
NG0549:527: 'jam dpal gsang ba sum cu pa'i rgyud las /
NG0549:528: ye shes kyi dal spyan drang zhing mchod pa'i le'u ste sum cu pa'o ///
NG0549:529: / rdo rje snying pos yang zhus pa /
NG0549:530: gshin don rnam pa ji ltar lags //
NG0549:533: 'jam dpal khro bos bka' stsal pa //
NG0549:534: gshin don rnam pa gsum du bstan //
NG0549:535: sems sbyang lus sbyang tsha tshwa'o //
NG0549:536: sems sbyang dkyil 'khor dgu dang ldan //
NG0549:537: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bsod nams gtor //
NG0549:538: gshed lcags drug po rgyud drug bsgral //
NG0549:539: rdo rje dbyings dang lam lnga bgrod //
NG0549:540: bgrod pa dbang dang mthar phyin bsreg / 'gro ba'i don la skul ba'o //
NG0549:541: gzugs brnyan rdul tshon bum pa dang *//
NG0549:542: me long dmar nag lding bu dang *//
NG0549:543: mda' gzhu zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NG0549:544: dri ma bca' ba spyi rgyu shes //
NG0549:545: bsod nams sbyin gtor dge ba'i las //
NG0549:547: gshed lcags khro bos brtul ba ste //
NG0549:548: phur thun bstabs dang bsreg par bya //
NG0549:549: rgyud drug sgral ba'i dkyil 'khor la //
NG0549:550: ngan song gnas su dug sbyang zhing *//
NG0549:551: mi yul zas gtad bsod nams tshogs //
NG0549:552: lha yi gnas su phan pa'i dbang *//
NG0549:553: de bzhin nus pa'i dbang yang bskur //
NG0549:554: rdo rje dbyings ni zhi khro yi //
NG0549:555: dkyil 'khor gnyis po bskyed cing sbyang *//
NG0549:556: rgyud drug sems bkug lus la bstim //
NG0549:557: 'dzab kyis bag chags sgrib pa sbyangs //
NG0549:558: skye ba'i rgyun ni gcad par bya //
NG0549:559: lam lnga bgrod pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NG0549:560: khro bo'i dal la gsol gdab 'jug / ye shes 'od kyi lus rtog sbyang *//
NG0549:561: rim par skor zhing byin brlabs te //
NG0549:562: 'byung ba'i sgo dgag tshogs lam non //
NG0549:563: bum par zhi khro gnyis la bstod //
NG0549:564: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs //
NG0549:565: mnyam par sbyor te sbyor lam non //
NG0549:566: thabs dang shes rab mda' gzhu yis //
NG0549:567: shes bya'i sgrib sbyang me long bstan //
NG0549:568: chos rnams rang gsal sems kyi don //
NG0549:569: rdo rje lta bu'i mthong lam non //
NG0549:570: med rtsa a yam zhi par spar //
NG0549:571: gsol gdab rim 'jug gtso bo yi //
NG0549:572: mkha' gsang dbyings nas sras su bskyed //
NG0549:573: zhi khro rdzogs pa'i dbang yang bskur //
NG0549:574: sa bcu bgrod de sgom pa'i lam //
NG0549:575: dmar po dar la sems ngo bstan //
NG0549:576: mthing nag la bzla byang bu bsreg / bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi smon lam gdab //
NG0549:577: 'gro don dbyings la skur bzhengs la //
NG0549:578: phyag rgyas spyan drangs brgyad kyis mchod //
NG0549:579: rdo rje 'chang gi sa la bstan //
NG0549:580: sems sbyangs rim pa rdzogs par bshad //
NG0549:581: lus sbyangs ro bsreg cho ga ni //
NG0549:582: brtul zhugs spyod pas ro langs la //
NG0549:583: khro bos drag po gshed dang dbral //
NG0549:584: dri yis byugs la ras kyis gril //
NG0549:585: gnas rnams zhugs mar sdong bu dang *//
NG0549:586: khams dang skye mched dag 'gyur bri //
NG0549:587: zhugs mar rol mos sna drangs la //
NG0549:588: dkyil 'khor bskor la dbus su bzhag / mchod rdzas bshams la 'jam dpal gyi //
NG0549:589: dkyil 'khor gnyis po bskyed la sbyang *//
NG0549:590: sdong po rnams la zhugs sbar la //
NG0549:591: 'jam dpal zhi ba'i lha la btab //
NG0549:592: bsreg khang brtsigs la me lha bskyed //
NG0549:593: zhi khro'i lha la rtog pa @#//
NG0549:595: dkar byang bla ma'i phyag tu dbul //
NG0549:596: nag byang me la bsreg par bya //
NG0549:597: rnam gsum smon lam rgya chen gdab //
NG0549:598: lus sbyang sgrib pa rdzogs par bshad //
NG0549:599: tsha tshwa gson don gshin don gnyis //
NG0549:600: bsod nams bdag gzhan thun mong ste //
NG0549:601: bdag don lha dang chos nyid rtog / thun mong zhi rgyas dbang drag ste //
NG0549:602: gshin don ngan song rnam gsum sbyang *//
NG0549:603: lta bas gtan phab lha bsgom la //
NG0549:604: rus pa sgrib sbyang rnam shes bsdu //
NG0549:605: yum lnga 'byung ba byin gyis brlabs //
NG0549:606: a las skor phor snang stong med //
NG0549:608: kun dang chos sku phyag rgya che //
NG0549:609: rgyu 'bras chos rdzogs gzhal yas su //
NG0549:610: zhi khro lha bskyed spyan drang mchod //
NG0549:611: rnam shes sku bstan thugs khar bstim //
NG0549:612: bstod cing smon lam rtags par bzhugs //
NG0549:613: tsha tshwa'i las rim rdzogs par bshad //
NG0549:614: rang byung bdud rtsi'i dngos grub ni //
NG0549:615: dang po khro bo bar chad brtul //
NG0549:616: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhengs gsol la //
NG0549:617: rigs su gyur pa'i thod pa lnga //
NG0549:618: rigs mthun sman la phyag rgyu dgod //
NG0549:619: srungs ma bos mchod bstim thog gzhom //
NG0549:620: zhi khro 'phrin las khrol bu sbyang *//
NG0549:621: nye ba'i bsnyen po de rdzogs nas //
NG0549:622: bdud rtsi 'khril pas brtag btsag sbyang *//
NG0549:624: sman rnams bsdus la mdangs gdon zhing *//
NG0549:626: a gro gar gyi brog dungs la //
NG0549:627: dgu pa'i sngags kyi gong bu sbyang *//
NG0549:628: rta mgrin dbang gi dkyil 'khor du //
NG0549:629: dbang bskur dbang grub blang bar bya //
NG0549:630: bde gshegs mchod la rang nyid bza' //
NG0549:631: sman rnams dam rdzas sna re la //
NG0549:632: yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pas //
NG0549:633: dngos grub khyad par can dag thob //
NG0549:635: 'jam dpal gsang ba sum cu pa'i rgyud las /
NG0549:636: gzhan don rnam pa gsum dang *//
NG0549:637: rang byung bdud rtsi'i dngos grub bsgrub pa'i le'u ste
NG0549:638: sum cu so gcig pa'o // // de nas bcom
NG0549:639: ldan 'das kyis 'khor la rgyud gtad pa 'di gsungs
NG0549:641: skyon med rnams dag chos kyi dbyings //
NG0549:642: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa la //
NG0549:643: ngo bo rol pa 'gag med du //
NG0549:644: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ru shar //
NG0549:645: thugs rjes 'gro ba drang ba'i phyir //
NG0549:646: brgyad khri bzhi stong chos kyang bstan //
NG0549:647: kun kyang drang ba'i thabs yin te //
NG0549:648: bde gshegs thugs kyis 'dul ba'i thabs //
NG0549:649: bde gshegs thugs kyi gsang brtol ba //
NG0549:650: gsang sngags bskyed rdzogs thabs lam grol //
NG0549:651: sgyu 'phrul drwa bas mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NG0549:652: byang chub thob pa'i don chen te //
NG0549:653: gsang don gsang ba sum cur ldan //
NG0549:654: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dam tshig dbang *//
NG0549:655: kun tshang 'brel bas man ngag rgyud //
NG0549:656: 'khor gyi dang po khyod la gtad //
NG0549:657: shes rab rig pa'i rtsal gyis long *//
NG0549:658: chags pa'i bsam pa brtan po bzung *//
NG0549:661: zab mo nges par 'byung ba'i dus //
NG0549:663: shakya dge slong skal can ni //
NG0549:664: lnga brgya phrag bcu'i dang po la //
NG0549:665: lho nub srin po'i gyad yul 'byung *//
NG0549:666: de la bstan pa'i char pa phab //
NG0549:667: mtshan don gsum dang ldan pa des //
NG0549:668: g.yu 'od gling du grags par nges //
NG0549:669: de phyir gsang ba'i rgyud don gtad //
NG0549:670: ces gsungs pa la 'khor rjes su yi rang zhing bstod do //
NG0549:671: 'jam dpal gsang ba sum cu pa'i rgyud las /
NG0549:672: gdams shing gtad pa'i le'u sum cu gnyis pa'o //
NG0549:673: // 'phags pa 'jam dpal man ngag gsang ba sum
NG0549:675: sgyu 'phrul drwa ba'i bka' ba gcod pa'i las thig zhi khro'i rtog pa dang bcas pa rdzogs so ///
NG0549:676: / rgya gar gyi sngags 'chang khrag 'thung nag po dang */
